long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Fast Arrow is a fun shooting game where we try to score points by shooting an arrow at a rotating target.
There is a rotating arrow in the game. We make accurate shots with this arrow. We also pay attention to the arrows on the target by shooting carefully. In this way, we get points by shooting arrows. We continue the game by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Fast Arrow has emerged as a fun shooter game for those who love skill games.
To swipe Install this extension to play the Fast Arrow game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
